unittitle_ssm: Archives of Irish America Irish Republicanism Collection
abstract_ssm: The collection documents Irish American support of civil rights and Republican activities in Northern Ireland, including anti-British demonstrations in the United States and activities in support of Irish Republicans subject to deportation proceedings in the United States.  Materials relating to Hunger Strikes and political prisoners in Ireland and the United States are also included.
